From the Smithing forum at EQ Traders:<br>
<br>
Shadowscream Steel Boots Made<br>
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br>
 I have to credit Amergyn with the idea to include water in the recipie. The recipie was:<br>
<br>
2 swirling shadows (unstacked)<br>
1 Humming Luclininte Hammer (mallet)<br>
1 Vah Shir Anvil<br>
1 Humming Orb<br>
1 Medium Banded Boot Mold<br>
1 Flask of Water<br>
<br>
REcipie Returns<br>
<br>
Shadowscream Steel Boots <br>
(AC 8, Dex 1, AGI 3, SvMagic 2, Wt. 2.0, Class: WAR CLR PAL RNG SHD BRD ROG SHM, Race ALL)<br>
Vah Shir Anvil<br>
Luclinite Mallet (Not humming any more)<br>
<br>
I can wear the boots (Dwarven Pally) so they really do fit small and the quest really can be done by non Vah SHir.<br>
<br>
I am petitioning the GM to see about the non humming thing. We'll see how it goes.<br>
<br>
